title: Antony Blinken ‘hopeful’ more hostages will be released but skeptical of Hamas
description: “Acts are what speak, not words, particularly from Hamas,” the U.S. secretary of state said in an interview on NBC News' "Meet the Press."

title: If McCarthy was speaker, how would he have responded to the Israel-Hamas war?
description:
During an exclusive interview with Meet the Press, former Speaker Kevin McCarthy (R-Calif.) says if he were still speaker he would have
sent aid to Israel, stood up to antisemitism and would
secure the southern border.
